ing and more to find the lethal shot.\n\nFeatures-\nManual and automatic reload\nPlay standing or seated\nPerk System\nKillstreaks\nProgression\nVariety of guns, melee equipment and grenades\nLeaderboard\nGame Modes- Free for All, Team Death Match/TDM Hardpoint, Search and Destroy, 4 Player Coop Zombies", "short_description": "*Now crossplay with all major VR Headsets\n\n Faster-paced gameplay provides an experience like no other, in this accessible, VR Shooter.\n\nGain the edge on the battlefield by running, jumping, sliding, crawling and more to find the lethal shot.\n\nFeatures-\nManual and automatic reload\nPlay standing or seated\nPerk System\nKillstreaks\nProgression\nVariety of guns, melee equipment and grenades\nLeaderboard\nGame Modes- Free for All, Team Death Match/TDM Hardpoint, Search and Destroy, 4 Player Coop Zombies"}]}, "developer_name": "OutsideIn Entertainment", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://alvogame.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://alvogame.com/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "OutsideIn Entertainment", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://alvogame.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1436351953220286"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SHOOTER", "ACTION", "HORROR"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "24637079082607278"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982623_2490683607802